{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban the use of face masks in schools",
        "additional_details": "I don't believe there is enough research about the effect that face masks can have on children in a school, so they should be banned until there is. The 'precautionary principle' should be applied.",
        "background": "Face coverings should be banned in schools as they can inhibit communication which could restrict learning and could create social stigma. ",
